and Chen, Zhijie
and Cai, Fei
and Wu, Jinsong
and Liu, Shengzong
and Liao, Zhining
and Liao, Zhifang",
title="Local Core Members Aided Community Structure Detection",
journal="Mobile Networks and Applications",
